			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				I found the cheaters quite entertaining :) <br> Usually I started off by ignoring them, when they came to kill me I just stood still and took it, till I died. Then I would come running back naked and harass em till they killed me again. Repeat. Eventually even PKer's get REALLY annoyed and will leave the game. Pick up corpse and items. Continue on your way. Laugh. <br>  <br> This is my prefered method for dealing with such things. Of course I find it entertaining and challenging to push some people past their limits of patience and into absolute frustration. <br>  <br> P.S. This works REALLY well on people with 'God' mode cheats. These are people with severe ego problems and don't take kindly to being unable to stop a pest... even when they can kill you with a single key-stroke. <br>  <br> Proud owner of Magius, 38th level Mage.  <br> Not one moment spent cheating. <br>  <br> Anyone find it odd that there was a bounty for my ear in that game? Considering how easy it was to aquire... :)		

